product.name: Automotive Floor Mats for Toyota C-HR 2018-2024 CHR, Heavy Duty TPE All Weather Car Floor Mats, 1st & 2nd Row Full Set Rubber Floor Liners, Anti Skid Car Mats for CHR, Black
product.description: We are a professional supplier of automotive accessories, with a variety of seat covers, floor mats, steering wheel covers and other products. If you need more car interiors, please enter our store to find more products you need. Product:Car floor mats,custom for 2018-2023 Toyota C-HR Material: TPE Product contains: 2 × Front floor mats 1 × Rear floor mats 1 × Installation Manual Compatibility The floor mats compatible with 2018-2024 TOYOTA C-HR All Weather Guard This set of floor mats can provide protection for your car all season,prevent your original car carpet from being damaged. It can also add fashion sense to the interior decoration of your car. Perfectly Fit Using the original car data 3D laser measurement, integrally molded,perfectly fit for the interior contours of your vehicle. TPE Material Heavy duty TPE material is environmentally friendly and safe, non-toxic and odorless, will not release toxic substances in summer or winter. Unique Groove Texture The groove on the surface of the floor mats can increase friction, and the channel can easily divert liquid, sand or snow, making it easy to clean. Waterproof The waterproof surface can resist liquid intrusion, and it is easy to clean.Just take out the floor mats,rinse it with a washer gun. Snap Button Design Match the anchors of the car floor,used to fix the floor mat to prevent it from sliding.
product.bullet_points:
• 【Perfect Fit for Toyota C-HR】Compatible with 2018-2024 Toyota C-HR, these floor mats provide full protection for the front and back with 3D laser scanning technology. Please remove old floor mats before installing new floor liners. Not for vehicles with vinyl floors.
• 【All-Weather Protection】These automotive floor mats can withstand any weather condition, protecting your vehicle's interior from rain, snow, sand, muddy water, stains, and more. Keep your car tidy and improve its resale value.
• 【High-Quality Material】Made with non-toxic and odorless 100% TPE material, these floor liners are environmentally friendly, wear-resistant, dirt-resistant, and easy to clean. You can be 100% safe even in extreme hot weather.
• 【Easy to Clean】The textured skid-resistant surface of these car floor mats is easy to clean. No need for a vacuum cleaner or chemicals, simply shake them out or spray them down with a hose.
• 【Non-Slip Design】With a card buckle that works with factory hooks and fasteners, these liners stay securely in place without additional fasteners, preventing sliding.
